l sconces, creating a welcoming atmosphere for gatherings. Incorporate personal touches like artwork or decorative mirrors to reflect light and expand the space visually. By harmonizing functionality with sophisticated design elements, your kitchen and dining area can become a stylish sanctuary for both culinary delights and social gatherings.','2024-07-17 08:28:24','2024-07-17 08:30:06'),(6,1,'Wooden Staircase Design','Interior','wooden-staircase-designs.jpg','','Do you love experimenting with styles and playing with different designs? Then, the perks of the floating wooden staircase design would catch your eyes instantly. If you are someone who wants a contemporary and minimalist design but also wants to keep a touch of classic style, this is one of the best wooden staircase designs you can go for.\r\n\r\nIt\'s a fantastic technique to achieve the ideal harmony between classic and modern design.\r\nYou are wrong if you think floating wooden staircases are not sturdy enough because they do not possess any firm structure. However, it is important to ensure that the home designers are opting for floating wooden staircases constructed by the International Residential Code regulations.\r\n\r\nAs per the IRC protocols, a stair thread must be capable of sustaining a load of 200 lbs. So, make sure that you are using a staircase that meets the requirements of IRC regulations to ensure your and your family\'s safety.','2024-07-17 08:33:40','2024-07-17 08:35:33'),(7,1,'Stylish couch with colorful pillows','Interior','pexels.jpg','','A stylish couch with colorful pillows can transform any living space into a vibrant and inviting area. Imagine a plush, modern sofa in a neutral shade like charcoal or beige, adorned with an array of pillows in bold hues and patterns. Vibrant colors such as deep teal, mustard yellow, and rich burgundy can infuse personality and warmth into the room. Mix textures like velvet, linen, and cotton for a tactile experience that enhances comfort. The co